
---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Paper Guides"
  description="Learn about the mission, community, and values behind Paper-Guides — a student-led open education project."
  canonical="https://paperguides.org/about"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen mt-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto p-10 shadow-xl rounded-2xl bg-[var(--baby-powder)] text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Welcome to <span style="color: var(--blue-highlight);">Paper-Guides</span>!
      </h1>
      <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
        Paper-Guides is a community-driven initiative built by students, for students — with one mission:
        <strong> make learning accessible and free</strong>. We're based in Nepal and strive to support
        learners everywhere by providing curated study resources.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
        We're completely <strong>open-source</strong> and transparent — anyone can contribute, improve, or
        suggest. You'll find us on{' '}
        <a
          href="https://github.com/chaulagainrupak/paper-guides"
          class="underline"
          style="color: var(--pink-highlight);"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          GitHub
        </a>{' '}
        and active across social platforms too.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 mt-6 mb-10">
        <a href="https://github.com/chaulagainrupak/paper-guides" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline" style="color: var(--pink-highlight);">GitHub Repository</a>
        <a href="https://instagram.com/paperguides.official" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline" style="color: var(--pink-highlight);">Instagram</a>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/U9fAnCgcu3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline" style="color: var(--blue-highlight);">Join us on Discord</a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Paper-Guides" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline" style="color: var(--blue-highlight);">YouTube Channel</a>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        To empower students by giving them access to high-quality, organised academic content — without
        charging a single rupee. We believe that shared knowledge fuels growth, and that learning should
        never be locked behind a paywall.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Community-Driven</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Paper-Guides is powered by students, volunteers, and curious minds who want to make education a bit
        easier for everyone. Whether it's uploading notes or helping organise content, every bit of help
        matters. Join our Discord to contribute or connect!
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">How It Works</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Just head over to the homepage, select your class or subject, and start browsing. You can also
        search topics directly. Everything is categorised for easier access and constantly updated with new
        materials.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Get Involved</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Want to contribute? You can submit notes, suggest topics, review shared content, or simply share
        Paper-Guides with your friends and school groups.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="mb-2">
        Email us at{' '}
        <span style="color: var(--pink-highlight);">
          <a href="mailto:contact@paperguides.org">contact@paperguides.org</a>
        </span>{' '}
        or{' '}
        <span style="color: var(--blue-highlight);">
          <a href="mailto:paperguides.official@proton.me">paperguides.official@proton.me</a>
        </span>
      </p>

      <p class="text-center mt-8 text-sm opacity-75">Thank you for supporting accessible education 🙌</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

